title: Snap Likely to Lose Users in 2019: Should Facebook Rejoice?
text: Per eMarketer, Snap (SNAP) will likely lose U.S.-based users in 2019, which spells good times for Facebook.

title: Regulatory Threats Higher Than Ever For Facebook, Amazon, Google
text: Facebook, Amazon and Google face a global regulatory push vs. Big Tech. Investors should take threats to their business models seriously.
